<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink103-kilavi">
        aṟattoṭunilai piṟantapiṉṉum varaivu nīṭiṟṟāka maṟṟoru kulamakaḷai varaiyuṅkoleṉṟu aiyuṟṟu cevili kuṟippaṟitatōḻi avaṭkuc colliyatu</p>      <p xml:lang="en">
        Spoken by the confidante who knew [her] intention to her - the foster mother - [she] being full of doubt, thinking, ‘because of the postponement of the marriage even after the state of truth was born, perhaps [he] married another community’s girl?’
</p> </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink108">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻi vēṇ ṭaṉṉai kaḻiya</l>
<l>muṇṭaka malarun taṇ kaṭaṟ cērppa</l>
<l>ṉentō ṭuṟantaṉa ṉāyi</l>
<l>ṉevaṉkoṉ maṟṟava ṉayanta tōḷē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>  Oh mother, please mother,</l>
<l>If the man from the shore of the cool ocean</l>
<l>Where Muṇṭakam blooms in the backwaters</l>
<l>Becomes one who abandons my shoulders,</l>
<l>What indeed will happen to those shoulders that he [once] desired?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
